//[Reference] 'Oh! I...I didn't expect to see you here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000100=あら！こんなところで会うなんて...
//[Reference] 'Uh... How did you even get here? Those devices are one time use and rather hard to make...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000200=それに...どうやってここへ？あの装置は1度しか使えないし、作るのも大変なはず...
//[Reference] 'It was that ^c:1486b0;scientist^c:pop;, wasn't it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000300=あの^c:1486b0;科学者^c:pop;でしょ？
//[Reference] 'I just wanted to bring ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; back, you know?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000400=私はただ、^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;に戻ってきてほしいの。
//[Reference] 'We all wanted that, but he just wouldn't come...kept talking about duty in his letters...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000500=私たちの、たったひとつの願い...それすらレイフは無視するのね...手紙で話すのは仕事のことばかり。
//[Reference] 'It was really hard to build something that could transfer objects from place to place!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000600=物を転送する装置の開発なんて、困難しかないっていうのに！
//[Reference] 'It was one-time-use too...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000700=おまけに使えるのは1度きり、っていうね...
//[Reference] 'How did she even fix it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000800=あの人、どうやって装置を直したの？
//[Reference] 'Well never mind. You're here now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000900=まあいいわ。あなたがここに来たわけだし。
//[Reference] 'At least one of you came willingly...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001000=自分から進んで来てくれる人もいるのは、分かった...
//[Reference] 'I'm here to bring ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; back.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001100=私は^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;を連れ戻しに来たの。
//[Reference] 'Oh...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001200=ん...
//[Reference] 'I shouldn't really help you, but...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001300=あなたの話に乗るのは気が引けるけど...
//[Reference] 'It's hard to see him so distressed.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001400=レイフが苦しむ姿を見るのはツライ。
//[Reference] 'Perhaps it was truly wrong of me to drag him back. Maybe he'll come back of his own free will someday...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001500=無理やり連れ戻すのは間違いだったのね。いつか自分の意志で帰ってくれるのを待つしかないわ...
//[Reference] 'Alright. I'll help you. It won't be easy though...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001600=分かった、手を貸すわ。簡単にはいかないけど...
//[Reference] 'We didn't want him to run away so we moved him somewhere...special...for the time being.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001700=レイフがどこかへ行くと困るから、少しのあいだ閉じ込......特別な場所に移動させましょう。
//[Reference] 'If you could get me a few items I should be able to pull together something that will whisk you past the barrier.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001800=アイテムを何個か持ってきてくれたら、バリアをすり抜けられる道具を作るわ。
//[Reference] 'There should be ^c:d03e37;five components^c:pop;. If you look around the ^c:1486b0;tree houses^c:pop; here you should find them.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001900=必要な^c:d03e37;材料は5つ^c:pop;。^c:1486b0;ツリーハウス^c:pop;周辺で見つかるはずよ。
//[Reference] 'We shouldn't be seen talking until you find the ^c:d03e37;five components^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002000=^c:d03e37;5つの材料^c:pop;が見つかるまでは、お互い知らんぷりしていましょう。
//[Reference] 'It would be bad if they suspected something was happening...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002100=みんなに怪しまれたらまずいことになる...
//[Reference] 'Yes, this looks like everything we need!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002200=やった、必要なものがそろったわ！
//[Reference] 'Now if you just give me a minu-'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002300=じゃあちょっと時間をちょうだ...
//[Reference] 'I apologise, the device initiated before I was quite ready.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002400=やだ、しっかり準備できる前に装置が始動しちゃった。
//[Reference] 'I hope I didn't cause you too much unnecessary concern...?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002500=えーと、まあ無事に動いてるっぽいってことで、使ってくれる...？
//[Reference] 'Who are you? Are you here to sell us something?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002600=あなたは誰？何か売りに来たの？
//[Reference] 'Just so you know, we don't have much money here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002700=念のために言っておくけど、私たちにはあまりお金がないの...
//[Reference] 'Too much being spent on personal projects and maintenence you see...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002800=個人的なプロジェクトとメンテナンスに使い過ぎちゃって...
//[Reference] 'Oh! You know ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002900=あっ！^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;を知ってる？
//TODO Translate [Reference] 'I hope he is doing well. I haven't seen him in a long time.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002910=
//[Reference] 'Well... I can send you back. But I don't think I have enough parts to visit myself...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003000=えっと...送り返してあげるわ。でも、私が行くにはパーツが足りないの...
//[Reference] 'Do you want to go?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003100=行きたいの？
//[Reference] 'Yep!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003200=うん！
//[Reference] 'No. I wanna look around.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003300=いや、ちょっと見て回りたい。
//[Reference] 'Oh! I...I didn't expect to see you here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003400=あら！こんなところで会うなんて...
//[Reference] 'Uh... How did you even get here?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003500=あの...ここにはよく来るの？
//[Reference] 'Did your ^c:1486b0;scientist^c:pop; give that device to you?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003600=^c:1486b0;科学者^c:pop;にその装置をもらったの？
//[Validate] Delete this comment if or when the translation is accurate.
//[Reference] 'I was sure that they would give it to ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003700=^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;にあげるものだと思ってたんだけど...
//[Validate] Delete this comment if or when the translation is accurate.
//[Reference] 'When you go back, can you tell them to work on it some more?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003800=もう一回行って、もっと頑張れって伝えてくれない？
